text: Koritnik may refer to: * Koritnik, mountain located in north-eastern Albania and south of Kosovo * Koritnik (Breza), village in the municipality of Breza, Bosnia and Herzegovina * Koritnik (Višegrad), village in the municipality of Višegrad, Bosnia and Herzegovina * Koritnik (Ivanjica), village in the municipality of Ivanjica in Serbia
title: Koritnik (disambiguation)
